  "title": "SelectiveBounds",
  "description": "Hides the ugly block selection outline when not relevant.",
  "body": "<h1>SelectiveBounds</h1>\n\n<p>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/selectivebounds\">\n<img alt=\"Modrinth\"\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Modrinth-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=modrinth&logoColor=000000&color=00AF5C\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/selectivebounds\">\n<img alt=\"CurseForge\"\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/CurseForge-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=curseforge&logoColor=000000&color=F16436\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/agxcvAdj2a\">\n<img alt=\"Discord\"\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Discord-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=discord&logoColor=000000&color=5865F2\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Luke100000/SelectiveBounds\">\n<img alt=\"Github\"\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Github-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=github&color=181717\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://crowdin.com/project/immersive-collection\">\n<img alt=\"Translate via Crowdin\"\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Crowdin-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=crowdin&color=2E3340\">\n</a>\n</p>\n\n<p>\nHides the ugly block selection outline when not relevant, especially on foliage and non-solid blocks.\n<br>\nThe outline is smartly hidden when the wrong tool is equipped, or the tool cannot mine at all.\nSneaking or building/destroying blocks temporarily shows it again.\nBehavior is fully configurable in <code>configs/selectivebounds.json</code>.\n</p>\n\n<img width=\"872\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=872,f=jpeg,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/selectivebounds/screenshots/screen.jpg\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<h1>Immersive Collection</h1>\n<p>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-armors\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Armors&description=A%20lot%20of%20unique%20and%20vanilla-faithful%20armor%20sets.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-armors/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Armors\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-aircraft\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Aircraft&description=A%20bunch%20of%20rustic%20aircraft%20to%20travel%2C%20transport%2C%20and%20explore%21&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-aircraft/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Aircraft\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-melodies\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Melodies&description=Play%20custom%20melodies%20on%20various%20instruments%20and%20annoy%20your%20friends%21&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-melodies/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Melodies\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-paintings\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Paintings&description=Drag%20and%20drop%2C%20pixelate%20and%20hang%20up%20beautiful%20art.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-paintings/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Paintings\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-optimization\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Optimization&description=A%20lightweight%20entity-tick-scheduler%20for%20doubling%20your%20TPS.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-optimization/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Optimization\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/selectivebounds\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=SelectiveBounds&description=Hides%20the%20ugly%20block%20selection%20outline%20when%20not%20relevant.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/selectivebounds/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"SelectiveBounds\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/man-of-many-planes\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Man%20of%20Many%20Planes&description=A%20set%20of%20additional%20aircraft%20for%20Immersive%20Aircraft%20with%20Create%20support%20in%20mind.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/man-of-many-planes/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Man of Many Planes\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-machinery\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Machinery&description=A%20bunch%20of%20rustic%20machinery%20to%20transport%2C%20mine%2C%20and%20automate%20things.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-machinery/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Machinery\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-furniture\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Furniture&description=Create%20custom%20and%20fancy%20furniture%20in-game%20or%20choose%20from%20a%20vast%20online%20library.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-furniture/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Furniture\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-gateways\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Gateways&description=Mysterious%2C%20long-forgotten%20portals%20scattered%20across%20the%20Overworld.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-gateways/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Gateways\"/>\n</a></p>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/common/pixel.png?immersive_pages_hash=82a3a213812cafe52a31627e1de56dd1\" alt=\"The page hash for easier page deployment.\"/>",
